Nardah teleport scrolls are obtained from all levels of Treasure Trails clues excluding beginner. The scroll is destroyed when used and teleports the player to Nardah.

Many players use these scrolls to get to areas farther into the desert, such as Sophanem or the Agility Pyramid. This teleport is also useful for the quest Icthlarin's Little Helper.

If the player has completed Spirits of the Elid, they can use this item to quickly teleport to near the Elidinis Statuette to quickly replenish their prayer points, run energy, special attack energy, and hitpoints. This can be ideal for combat activities that require frequent restoration, such as Barrows.

A player using a scroll to teleport.
